descriptor.name: Channelier Hardware Nilanjan Industrial Grinder
descriptor.short_desc: Nilanjan Industrial Grinder – Built for performance and durability, this high-power mixer grinder delivers exceptional grinding efficiency for heavy-duty industrial and commercial use. Rugged, reliable, and easy to operate.
descriptor.long_desc: The Nilanjan Industrial Grinder is engineered to meet the toughest grinding demands of industrial kitchens and commercial settings. Powered by a robust high-torque motor, it handles large quantities of spices, grains, and other tough ingredients with ease. Its heavy-duty stainless steel construction ensures long-lasting durability even under continuous use. Designed for efficiency and safety, the grinder features precision blades, multiple speed settings, and thermal overload protection. Whether for large-scale food preparation, spice grinding, or ingredient processing, the Nilanjan Industrial Grinder guarantees consistent performance, minimal downtime, and easy maintenance. An essential companion for businesses that demand power, reliability, and uncompromised results.

descriptor.name: Channelier Hardware Industrial Chilli Grinding Machine, 200-500 kg/hr, Hammer Mill
descriptor.code: Channelier Hardware Industrial Chilli Grinding Machine, 200-500 kg/hr, Hammer Mill
descriptor.short_desc:
Manufacturer & Supplier of Chilly Grinding Plant we provide this plant with full facilities including others tolls whihc are used in running this machine smothly.We looking buyer of Chilly Grinding Plant from all over world .

Hammer mill is economical unit designed for all types of spices for time saving operation.

All spices passes through a wide feed hopper into the grinding chamber.

the swinging hammers, in the rotating hammer rotor, crushes materials at the stationery liners before passes through a screen and rotating hammers. The ground material is continuously sucked by a powerful air blower through screen and conveyed though the pipe line into the cyclone separator for bagging. The air blower maintains constant atmospheric cool air flow in the mill chamber in order to obtain a cool & quality product and continuously cleans the screen, thus increases the output of the ground material. The particles size of the ground material can be varied by a large range of sieves with the desired opening. The dust & ground material is gets separated in the cyclone separator. Top of the cyclone air balloon is fitted. Air balloon separates clean air & dust. The dust gets collated in air balloon. As soon as air balloon shacked the dust dropped into the cyclone separator and get collected from bottom of the cyclone separator.

descriptor.name: Channelier Hardware Sanders FORMAT-4 Finish 1353 Wide Belt Sander, For Industrial, Fully Automatic
descriptor.code: Channelier Hardware Sanders FORMAT-4 Finish 1353 Wide Belt Sander, For Industrial, Fully Automatic
descriptor.short_desc: The finish 1352 modular and 1353 modular wide-belt sanding machines impress with their unique flexibility. Either as a 2 or 3 belt machine – you can decide the individual equipment and configuration of the processing units. The free aggregate configuration option enables the optimal adaption to your requirements which ensures maximum efficiency and maximum time saving.
descriptor.long_desc: The FORMAT-4 Finish 1353 Wide Belt Sander is the ultimate solution for industrial-grade surface finishing, offering fully automatic operation for consistent, high-quality sanding results. Designed for professional woodworking, furniture manufacturing, and industrial panel processing, this machine features a wide belt system capable of handling large workpieces with superior precision. With advanced digital controls, adjustable sanding pressures, and multiple sanding units, the Finish 1353 ensures perfect surface smoothness while maximizing operational efficiency. Heavy-duty construction, a powerful motor, and a vibration-free belt drive system make it ideal for continuous use in demanding production environments. Easy-to-use interfaces, automatic thickness calibration, and safety mechanisms enhance user experience and minimize downtime, making the FORMAT-4 Finish 1353 a top choice for industries that demand excellence in every finish.

descriptor.long_desc: The Industrial Dual Action Sanders, models 27330 and ES009, are engineered for professional surface preparation and finishing applications. Designed with dual-action (random orbital) motion, they deliver an ultra-smooth finish by combining both rotary and orbital movements, significantly reducing surface swirls and marks. Perfect for wood, metal, automotive, and composite materials, these sanders offer high-speed operation with adjustable speed control for precision work. Built with robust materials, ergonomic handles, and powerful pneumatic or electric motors, they ensure consistent performance even during extended industrial use. Low vibration levels and advanced dust extraction ports contribute to user comfort and cleaner work environments. Whether for rough sanding, fine finishing, or polishing tasks, the 27330 and ES009 models are reliable tools for heavy-duty industrial operations.
